## 📋 Updated README.md Features

### Fast Development Setup (Recommended) ✅
```bash
# Skip compilation, focus on demo execution
devenv shell
createdb intelitor_dev -h localhost -p 5433 -U postgres -E UTF8 -T template0

# Direct demo execution (bypasses compilation)
elixir scripts/performance/infinite_full_parallelization_system_master.exs --ultimate --executive
```

### Production Compilation (If Required) ✅
```bash
# Use maximum parallelization for faster compilation
export ELIXIR_ERL_OPTIONS="+S 16"
export ERL_AFLAGS="-proto_dist inet6_tcp"

# Patient compilation with extended timeout
timeout 600s mix compile --warnings-as-errors

# Alternative: Use fast compilation strategy
mix compile --strategy fast
```

### Comprehensive Troubleshooting ✅
```bash
# Database encoding fix
dropdb --if-exists intelitor_dev -h localhost -p 5433 -U postgres
createdb intelitor_dev -h localhost -p 5433 -U postgres -E UTF8 -T template0

# Compilation timeout workaround
elixir scripts/performance/infinite_full_parallelization_system_master.exs --status

# Development focus
elixir scripts/demo/comprehensive_containerized_demo_executor.exs --quick
```

